====== IBM PC/AT 5170 (1984) ======





===== Features =====



  * CPU: Intel 80286 6 MHz

  * RAM: 512 KB (up to 3 MB)

  * ROM: 64 kb

  * Text Modes: 80 x 24 / 40 x 24

  * Graphic Modes: 640 x 350 [EGA mode]

