====== Jupiter Cantab Jupiter Ace (1981) ======





===== Features =====



  * CPU: Zilog Z80A 3.25 MHz

  * RAM: 3 kb (up to 51 kb)

  * ROM: 8 kb

  * Text Modes: 32 columns x 24 lines

  * Graphic Modes: 64 x 48

  * Colors: Monochrome

