====== Sharp Pocket Computer 1251 (1982) ======





===== Features =====



  * CPU: CMOS SC61860 (8 bits) 576 kHz

  * RAM: 4 KB

  * ROM: 24 KB

  * Text Modes: 1 line x 24 char. 5 x 7 dot matrix

  * Graphic Modes: None

