====== Nintendo Virtual Boy (1995) ======





===== Features =====



  * CPU: NEC V810 32-bit RISC Processor at 20 MHz

  * DRAM: 1 MB

  * SRAM: 512 KB

  * Display: RTI Scanning LED Array (SLA) P4; 384 x 224 Resolution

  * Sound: 16-bit Stereo

  * Controllers: 6 buttons and 2-D pads

